# Schema Types

Defines types for schema validation errors.

## Types

### SchemaViolation

Fields:
- `FilePath` (string) - Path to the file with the violation.
- `Field` (string) - The field name that failed validation.
- `Message` (string) - Human-readable description.
- `Severity` (string) - "error" or "warning".
